    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN354-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. paraṇar.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div> 
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN354">
<l>araicutalai variṉu maṭaṅka lāṉā</l>
<l>niraikā ḻeḵka nīriṉ mūḻkap</l>
<l>puraiyōr cērnteṉat tantaiyum peyarkkum</l>
<l>vayalamar kaḻaṉi vāyiṟ poykaik</l>
<l>kayalār nārai yukaitta vāḷai</l>
<l>puṉalāṭu makaḷir vaḷamaṉai yoyyu</l>
<l>mūrkavi ṉiḻappavum varuvatu kollō</l>
<l>cuṇaṅkaṇin teḻiliya vaṇaintēn tiḷamulai</l>
<l>vīṅkiṟaip paṇaittōṇ maṭantai</l>
<l>māṉpiṇai yaṉṉa makiḻmaṭa nōkkē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if a king comes against [him], because [his] great [warriors]</l>
<l>have joined to submerge [their] blades with shafts(?) in a row in the water</l>
<l>that do not end yielding(?), [her] father too(?) will drive [him] away.</l>
<l>Even if the beauty of [this] village is lost,</l>
<l>where women bathing in the flood carry [back] to [their] prosperous houses</l>
<l>the Vāḷai fish moved [out] by the heron feeding on Āral fish</l>
<l>in the pond at the [flood] gate of the paddy field lying in the fields,</l>
<l>  will it come [again],</l>
<l>the delighted youthful look, like [that of] a doe,</l>
<l>of the girl with bamboo shoulders with plump joints,</l>
<l>[her] young breasts rising ? that are graceful, adorned with beauty spots?  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
